name: The Best of 2013
description:
Well everybody, here is the first upload of 2014 from this channel, and also the last video featuring footage from 2013, with the exception of Paine Field videos, since I've got a few more to upload. I hope you guys enjoy this reflection on such an awesome year of aviation! Thanks for all the support :)

Also: My FSX Movie "The Future" won second place in FSXAviation1 and 1506jet's video contest :)

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
_____________________________________________________

Check out my previous video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=05JApNQFq18
(Best Engine Sounds of 2013)

Music is "Achilles", "Thinking of You" and "Egmont Overture Finale" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
